
== Dolphin Hugger ==

Term used by scientists and academics referring to early career would-be marine biologists. Particularly, this applies to people that are studying marine biology to be dolphin trainers, and are not seriously interested in studying science. Note: this term carries a strong negative connotation. 

“Oy, I have a marine biology class full of dolphin huggers.”

